    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S features the M96 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The Viscous Map AWD system ensures exceptional mechanical grip, while the wide-body chassis and Porsche Stability Management (PSM) provide a balanced, communicative driving experience. It is equipped with four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal management. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly. Showing honest wear consistent with a well-maintained driver, this C4S remains a visceral, analog masterpiece ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 36500.0,
